name: Rice AI
description: RICE AI aims to unlock the $45 trillion future robotics workforce by achieving the next AI breakthrough—AGI robots—through a decentralized ecosystem. Backed by Rice Robotics, a Hong Kong-based robotics company with over 500 robots deployed worldwide, it has raised $7 million in the last funding round in 2023. Rice Robotics already has already laid the foundation for RICE AI to succeed.
